WEBVTT

00:01.068 --> 00:02.703
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON "WEEDS"...</i>

00:02.736 --> 00:04.204
I AM RUNNING FOR CITY COUNCIL.

00:04.238 --> 00:06.273
MY LITTLE BUDDY OVER HERE
IS A FIRST‐TIMER.

00:06.306 --> 00:07.875
DO YOU HAVE
ANY STUDENT DISCOUNTS?

00:07.908 --> 00:09.409
Nancy:
"LACY LAPLANTE."

00:09.443 --> 00:11.778
WHY NOT JUST CALL ME
"MARY JANE DEALER"?

00:11.812 --> 00:13.046
THIS IS HYDRO.

00:13.080 --> 00:14.581
WE ARE GOOD TO GROW.

00:14.615 --> 00:19.853
