00:21.455 --> 00:23.290
FUCK ALL OF YOU!
FUCK ALL OF YOU!

00:23.323 --> 00:24.725
AAH! AAH!

00:24.758 --> 00:28.095
Victor: ARAM KESHESHIAN,
NORTH SIDE ARMENIAN POWER.

00:28.128 --> 00:29.930
YOU ARE NEW
TO THE NEIGHBORHOOD.

00:29.963 --> 00:31.565
THIS IS TO SAY "GOODBYE."

00:31.598 --> 00:34.835
HUSKEROOS ‐‐ IT'S A CLOTHING
LINE FOR LARGER CHILDREN.

00:34.868 --> 00:37.804
MY DAUGHTER IS NOT MODELING
FAT CLOTHES.

00:37.838 --> 00:39.907
Y'ALL ARE
GATHERED HERE TODAY

00:39.940 --> 00:44.444
TO JOIN THESE TWO
IN HOLY...MATRIMONY!

00:44.478 --> 00:48.282
