A WHOLE BOX OF TESTS.

01:58.652 --> 02:00.888
SHE'S GONNA TAKE
ANOTHER ONE.

02:00.921 --> 02:02.856
YOU'RE HUMILIATING HER.

02:02.890 --> 02:04.124
SILAS, SHE'S FINE.

02:04.157 --> 02:05.392
SHE'S PREGNANT!

02:05.425 --> 02:09.296
WELL,
WE'RE GOING TO CONFIRM THAT.

02:09.329 --> 02:11.932
WHY DO YOU HAVE
A HOME‐PREGNANCY TEST?

02:11.965 --> 02:13.800
DO YOU WANT ME
TO KILL YOU?

02:13.834 --> 02:15.669
I CAN'T PEE.

02:15.702 --> 02:17.037
DRINK SOME WATER.

02:18.772 --> 02:20.240
I WAS JUST
ASKING A QUESTION.

02:20.274 --> 02:22.009
I ASK THE QUESTIONS.
FINE.

02:22.042 --> 02:23.343
I'M THE MOTHER.
OKAY.

02:23.377 --> 02:25.879
HOW DID THIS HAPPEN?
YOU DON'T WANT TO HEAR IT.

02:25.913 --> 02:27.047
OH, BUT I REALLY DO.

02:27.080 --> 02:28.348
