02:28.382 --> 02:30.784
I WOULD SAY IT WAS
THREE WEEKS AGO IN MY ROOM...

02:30.817 --> 02:31.885
DOGGIE STYLE.

02:31.919 --> 02:33.320
WHEN I PULLED OUT,
THE CONDOM WAS GONE.

02:33.353 --> 02:34.888
MEGAN HAS
REALLY STRONG MUSCLES.

02:34.922 --> 02:36.390
MUST HAVE SUCKED THE THING
RIGHT OFF.

02:36.423 --> 02:37.424
AH, AH, AH, AH.

02:37.457 --> 02:38.959
STOP. STOP. STOP.

02:38.992 --> 02:40.093
YOU ASKED.

02:40.127 --> 02:41.795
YOU WANT TO BE
THE COOL MOM.

02:41.828 --> 02:42.930
NO. NO, I DON'T.

02:42.963 --> 02:45.866
