NOWHERE ON THAT LIST.

02:52.206 --> 02:56.844
WELL, I HOPE "GRANDMA"
IS ON THAT LIST.

02:56.877 --> 02:59.246
Dean:
THIS IS ALL SO EXCITING.

02:59.279 --> 03:01.281
ISN'T THIS EXCITING?
IT'S EXCITING.

03:01.315 --> 03:03.450
