TO BE NERVOUS ABOUT.

03:06.920 --> 03:07.955
Woman: HODES.

03:07.988 --> 03:09.423
ISABEL HODES.

03:09.456 --> 03:10.791
SHE'S RIGHT HERE.

03:10.824 --> 03:12.526
