OF SELF‐ESTEEM.

03:35.315 --> 03:38.051
TRY NOT TO GET TASERED
THIS TIME.

03:39.253 --> 03:42.856
YOUR GIRL'S IN THERE
RIGHT NOW.

03:42.890 --> 03:44.758
THAT'S WONDERFUL.

03:44.791 --> 03:45.926
YOU WANT A MAPLE BAR?

03:45.959 --> 03:47.261
NO. NO, THANK YOU.

03:47.294 --> 03:50.764
I'M GETTING A CORN‐SYRUP
CONTACT HIGH JUST SITTING HERE.

03:51.932 --> 03:54.935
"I'M COMFORTABLE
IN MY SKIN.

03:54.968 --> 03:57.905
