04:10.584 --> 04:11.885
HUSKEROO LETS YOU BE YOU!

04:11.919 --> 04:14.821
HUSKEROO LETS YOU BE YOU!

04:14.855 --> 04:16.156
ISABEL!

04:16.190 --> 04:18.058
MOM?

04:18.091 --> 04:21.061
SHE'S FANTASTIC.

04:22.829 --> 04:24.831
♪♪ DA DA‐DA LA‐LA
DA DA DA‐DA ♪♪

