A BURGER KING

04:50.490 --> 04:52.059
IN THE MIDDLE
OF FUCKING McDONALD'S,

04:52.092 --> 04:53.760
EXCEPT RONALD IS THIS
TRACK‐SUIT‐WEARING MOTHERFUCKER

04:53.794 --> 04:56.063
NAMED BEHZAD WITH A LAST NAME
THAT LOOKS LIKE AN EYE CHART,

04:56.096 --> 04:57.397
READY TO CUT YOUR DICK OFF

04:57.431 --> 04:59.199
AND MAIL IT
IN FOUR DIFFERENT DIRECTIONS.

04:59.233 --> 05:01.101
WE'RE BUCK‐NAKED
IN FRONT OF GEORGE BUSH

05:01.134 --> 05:03.003
WITH OUR DICK
IN HIS DAUGHTER'S MOUTH.

05:03.036 --> 05:04.204
ENOUGH WITH THE DICKS.

05:04.238 --> 05:07.641
WHAT IF THOSE HOUSES
ACCIDENTALLY BURN DOWN?

05:07.674 --> 05:09.009
OKAY. NO, THANK YOU.

05:09.042 --> 05:10.811
NO, THANK YOU, HONEY.

05:10.844 --> 05:12.846
WE GOT A HOUSE FULL OF PLANTS,
LACY.

05:12.880 --> 05:14.915
WE NEED TO PACK THEM UP
IN SOIL,

05:14.948 --> 05:17.050
RENT US SOME U‐HAULS,
AND GET THE FUCK OUT.

05:17.084 --> 05:18.886
WE HAVE TO MOVE.

05:18.919 --> 05:20.754
HEY, CAN WE AT LEAST HIRE
THE GUYS

05:20.787 --> 05:22.155
OUTSIDE OF HOME DEPOT
TO MOVE US?

05:22.189 --> 05:23.657
