05:35.569 --> 05:38.138
I'LL TAKE CARE OF IT.

05:41.808 --> 05:43.110
[ INHALES AND EXHALES ]

05:43.143 --> 05:45.879
BRIDGEPORT, CONNECTICUT,
LIFEGUARDING.

05:45.913 --> 05:48.348
OOH.

05:48.382 --> 05:49.750
Silas: CHARLIE?

05:49.783 --> 05:52.786
FLORENCE?

05:52.819 --> 05:55.122
ELLEN?

05:56.823 --> 05:58.759
NO. NO.

05:58.792 --> 06:00.194
OKAY.

06:01.895 --> 06:05.399
