IN A RESIDENTIAL CUL‐DE‐SAC.

06:43.003 --> 06:45.606
IT'S A SPECIAL KIND
OF BAKERY.

06:45.639 --> 06:46.740
SPECIAL HOW?

06:46.773 --> 06:51.645
SPECIAL IN THAT WE WON'T
NECESSARILY BAKE ANYTHING THERE.

06:51.678 --> 06:55.449
WHAT ARE YOU GOING TO DO IN
THIS BAKERY IF YOU DO NOT BAKE?

06:55.482 --> 06:57.918
WE'RE GOING ‐‐
UM, THAT IS TO SAY,

06:57.951 --> 07:02.723
