HIS GIRLFRIEND PREGNANT...

07:53.941 --> 07:55.909
DOGGIE STYLE.

07:55.943 --> 07:58.011
WHAT?
THEY'RE TELLING
HER PARENTS TODAY.

07:58.045 --> 08:00.447
I SHOULD BE AT HOME
WAITING FOR HIM,

08:00.480 --> 08:03.183
BUT I CAN'T
BECAUSE I HAVE THIS PROBLEM.

08:03.217 --> 08:07.421
I HAVE FIRES IN TWO HOUSES,
MR. BOTWIN.

08:11.458 --> 08:13.760
MR. SCOTTSON.

08:15.829 --> 08:18.131
I'VE GOT TO GET
BACK TO WORK.

08:18.165 --> 08:19.466
OH.

08:22.703 --> 08:25.038
GO BE A MOM.

08:26.874 --> 08:30.143
