MORALLY BANKRUPT DEGENERATE.

12:51.271 --> 12:54.107
IS THAT WHAT YOU PULLED ME
OUT OF THE YESHIVA TO TELL ME?
YESHIVA?

12:54.141 --> 12:56.410
YEAH, AT HaMIDRASH LaTORAH,

12:56.443 --> 13:00.013
WHERE I'M A FULL‐TIME
RABBINICAL STUDENT,

13:00.047 --> 13:03.250
