13:26.006 --> 13:27.741
SHANE'S...
GOING THROUGH CHANGES.

13:27.774 --> 13:28.976
HE'S EXPERIMENTING.

13:29.009 --> 13:30.010
EXPERIMENTING?

13:30.043 --> 13:31.445
HE'S MASTURBATING.

13:31.478 --> 13:32.379
OH.

13:32.412 --> 13:34.848
IT'S AN AWKWARD TIME
FOR A YOUNG MAN.

13:34.882 --> 13:36.750
