13:48.795 --> 13:49.930
WATCHING YOU.

13:49.963 --> 13:50.931
PRINCIPAL DODGE?

13:50.964 --> 13:52.599
THE SHAME.

13:52.633 --> 13:54.468
YEAH, THE SHAME.

13:56.737 --> 13:58.372
[ CHUCKLES ]

13:58.405 --> 14:00.807
[ LAUGHS ]

14:00.841 --> 14:03.777
SO, YOU DIDN'T TAKE HIM
TO SEE JADE?

14:03.810 --> 14:05.445
I TOOK HIM
TO A CHINESE RESTAURANT.

14:05.479 --> 14:06.747
[ LAUGHTER ]

14:06.780 --> 14:09.816
WE'RE GONNA LET YOUNG SHANE OFF
WITH A WARNING.
THAT'S SUPER.

14:09.850 --> 14:11.151
AND WE'RE NOT GONNA MENTION ‐‐
YOU KNOW.

14:11.185 --> 14:12.920
YOUR FATHER
IN THE BEE COSTUME.

14:12.953 --> 14:14.488
HAVE A GOOD DAY,
MR. BOTWIN.

14:14.521 --> 14:15.756
YEAH.

14:15.789 --> 14:18.125
HELLO,
MY NAME IS DEBRA GEHRINGER,

14:18.158 --> 14:21.762
CALLING ON BEHALF OF AGRESTIC
CITIZENS FOR CHANGE...

14:21.795 --> 14:23.530
WE ARE MAKING
A COURTESY CALL

14:23.564 --> 14:25.766
TO REMIND CONCERNED VOTERS
LIKE YOURSELF

14:25.799 --> 14:27.835
ABOUT THE DEBATE
FOR CITY COUNCIL...

14:27.868 --> 14:30.137
HI, THIS IS NANCY BOTWIN,
AND I'M CALLING

14:30.170 --> 14:32.539
ON BEHALF OF AGRESTIC,
UM, CITIZENS FOR CHANGE.

14:32.573 --> 14:35.542
WOULD YOU LIKE AGRESTIC
TO BE A DRUG‐FREE COMMUNITY?

14:35.576 --> 14:39.713
NANCY, PUT A LITTLE MORE PERK
IN YOUR PITCH.

14:45.919 --> 14:49.156
HI,
CAN I SPEAK TO MR. FUKHUSEN?

14:49.189 --> 14:50.958
I CAN'T DO THIS, CELIA.

14:50.991 --> 14:52.226
WHAT?

14:52.259 --> 14:55.229
WE'RE JUST LETTING PEOPLE KNOW
ABOUT THE DEBATE.

14:55.262 --> 14:57.998
"DEBRA GEHRINGER,
AGRESTIC CITIZENS FOR CHANGE"?

14:58.031 --> 15:00.000
WELL,
I CAN'T JUST SAY IT'S ME.

15:00.033 --> 15:01.902
YOU KNOW,
THAT WOULD BE TOO...

15:01.935 --> 15:02.970
HONEST?

15:03.003 --> 15:04.304
...LEADING.

15:04.338 --> 15:08.175
WE'RE TRYING TO LET THE VOTERS
DECIDE FOR THEMSELVES.

15:08.208 --> 15:10.444
I GUESS IT'S ONLY
MARGINALLY DELUSIONAL.

15:10.477 --> 15:13.213
YOU KNOW, THERE'S NO GUN
POINTED AT YOUR HEAD.

15:13.247 --> 15:14.581
IF YOU CAN'T MAKE TIME

15:14.615 --> 15:17.684
FOR THE PRESSING PROBLEMS
OF GREATER AGRESTIC ‐‐

15:17.718 --> 15:18.886
THAT'S EXACTLY IT.

15:18.919 --> 15:20.888
I CAN'T MAKE TIME.
I'VE GOT PROBLEMS AT HOME.

15:20.921 --> 15:22.022
REALLY?

15:22.055 --> 15:23.624
DO YOU WANT TO TALK
ABOUT IT?

15:23.657 --> 15:26.527
I DON'T WANT TO TALK ABOUT IT.
I JUST WANT TO GO HOME.

15:26.560 --> 15:29.730
YOU KNOW, I TELL YOU ABOUT
MY HUSBAND'S UNEMPLOYMENT,

15:29.763 --> 15:33.400
MY DAUGHTER BEING THE FACE
OF AMERICA'S TRANS FAT,

15:33.433 --> 15:35.869
SO...

15:35.903 --> 15:39.673
TELL ME
WHAT'S GOING ON WITH YOU.

15:39.706 --> 15:41.141
PLEASE, NANCY.

15:41.175 --> 15:43.010
CELIA ‐‐
AREN'T WE FRIENDS?

15:43.043 --> 15:44.745
I JUST WANT TO GO.

15:44.778 --> 15:46.213
YOU CAN'T EVEN SAY IT.

15:46.246 --> 15:48.916
YOU DON'T WANT TO BE
MY FRIEND.

15:48.949 --> 15:52.586
EVERYTHING IS NOT ABOUT YOU,
CELIA.

15:54.955 --> 15:56.490
WHAT THE FUCK
ARE YOU DOING?!

15:56.523 --> 15:57.591
BE MY FRIEND!

15:57.624 --> 15:59.893
LET GO
OF MY FUCKING HAIR!

15:59.927 --> 16:01.195
BE MY FRIEND!

16:01.228 --> 16:02.996
LET GO
OF MY FUCKING HAIR!

16:03.030 --> 16:05.432
BE MY GODDAMN,
MOTHERFUCKING FRIEND!

16:05.465 --> 16:06.567
OW! YOU'RE INSANE!

16:06.600 --> 16:07.601
SELFISH!

16:07.634 --> 16:09.403
SELFISH! SELFISH!

16:14.775 --> 16:16.243
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

16:16.276 --> 16:19.213
YOU TWO
ARE JUST LIKE SISTERS.

16:19.246 --> 16:22.082
[ CRICKETS CHIRPING ]

16:23.584 --> 16:25.185
HEY, DEANO.

16:25.219 --> 16:26.587
HEY, YOU GOT THE LATE SHIFT.

16:26.620 --> 16:28.789
DON'T YOU HAVE A DEBATE
WITH MY WIFE TOMORROW?

16:28.822 --> 16:31.391
OH, YEAH, THE DEBATE THINGY.

16:31.425 --> 16:33.093
WHAT'S ON THE BOOB?

16:33.126 --> 16:34.428
YEAH,
AS YOUR CAMPAIGN MANAGER,

16:34.461 --> 16:36.330
I SHOULD TELL YOU
SHE'S BEEN PRACTICING ALL WEEK.

16:36.363 --> 16:37.798
WELL,
SHE'S WASTING HER TIME.

16:37.831 --> 16:39.032
NOBODY GOES TO THOSE THINGS.

16:39.066 --> 16:40.934
AND BESIDES,
I'M GREAT AT DEBATING.

16:40.968 --> 16:42.703
GO AHEAD.
ASK ME A QUESTION.

16:42.736 --> 16:44.972
UM, MR. WILSON,
WHAT ZONING LAWS

16:45.005 --> 16:48.575
DO YOU PLAN TO ENACT
TO COMBAT SUBURBAN SPRAWL?

16:48.609 --> 16:49.610
[ FARTS ]

16:49.643 --> 16:50.777
NEXT QUESTION.

16:50.811 --> 16:52.713
YOU'RE NOT EVEN WORRIED.
WORRIED?

16:52.746 --> 16:54.548
NOBODY LIKES YOUR WIFE.
YOU DON'T EVEN LIKE HER.

16:54.581 --> 16:56.617
I COULD STAND UP
AT THAT PODIUM TOMORROW NIGHT

16:56.650 --> 16:59.152
AND TAKE A SHIT ON ONE OF THOSE
MAKE‐A‐WISH CANCER KIDS,

16:59.186 --> 17:01.889
AND PEOPLE WILL STILL VOTE FOR
ME 'CAUSE THEY HATE YOUR WIFE.

17:01.922 --> 17:03.490
AND I'M LIKABLE.

17:03.524 --> 17:05.859
YOU ALMOST
MAKE ME FEEL BAD FOR CELIA.

17:05.893 --> 17:07.895
TELL HER THAT.
MAYBE SHE'LL FUCK YOU.

17:07.928 --> 17:09.396
SEE,
I'M ON YOUR SIDE, BUDDY.

17:09.429 --> 17:11.031
VOTE FOR ME.

17:15.869 --> 17:18.105
<i>HABLA.</i>

17:18.138 --> 17:20.674
<i>HAY MOMENTOS</i>
<i>EN LA VIDA DE...</i>

17:20.707 --> 17:21.808
[ STATIC ON TV ]

17:21.842 --> 17:23.777
<i>CADA SITUACIóN</i>
<i>ES TAN GRAVE</i>

17:23.810 --> 17:24.978
<i>QUE DEBEMOS A...</i>

17:25.012 --> 17:26.547
[ STATIC ]

17:26.580 --> 17:29.016
BITCHIN'.

17:30.117 --> 17:32.286
DOUG, YOU THINK
IT'S THE CIRCUIT BREAKER?

17:32.319 --> 17:33.387
[ FARTS ]

17:33.420 --> 17:34.855
NEXT QUESTION.

17:34.888 --> 17:36.190
COME ON, BOY.
ZIP IT UP.

17:36.223 --> 17:38.725
I'M TRYING, HEYLIA. YOU GOT
TO INHALE MORE OR SOMETHING.

17:38.759 --> 17:40.093
NOW, I AIN'T THAT FAT.

17:40.127 --> 17:42.196
JUST PUT SOME BACKBONE
INTO IT.

17:42.229 --> 17:43.997
COME ON.
ONE, TWO, THREE.

17:44.031 --> 17:45.866
THAT'S IT.
ALL RIGHT.

17:45.899 --> 17:46.967
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

17:47.000 --> 17:48.669
WHOO! THAT'S HIM!
THAT'S HIM!

17:48.702 --> 17:51.071
GIVE ME THE VANILLA EXTRACT.
WHAT DO YOU NEED THAT FOR?

17:51.104 --> 17:52.973
JUST GIVE IT TO ME.
HE LIKES BAKED GOODS.

17:54.508 --> 17:56.343
OKAY. OOH.

17:56.376 --> 17:57.544
ALL RIGHT, HERE.

17:57.578 --> 17:59.046
HOW DO I LOOK?
HOW DO I LOOK?

17:59.079 --> 18:01.248
YOU LOOK GOOD.
ALL RIGHT.

18:03.016 --> 18:04.051
OH, SHIT.

18:04.084 --> 18:05.886
YOU AIN'T JOSEPH.

18:05.919 --> 18:07.221
YOU GOT ANY COFFEE?

18:07.254 --> 18:09.990
CONRAD,
GET THE CHILD SOME COFFEE.

18:10.023 --> 18:11.225
MAKE IT BLACK.

18:11.258 --> 18:12.759
SHE LIKES IT BLACK,
CONRAD.

18:13.927 --> 18:15.062
LATE NIGHT?

18:15.095 --> 18:17.097
HELPING MY FRIEND LACY OUT.

18:17.130 --> 18:19.499
SOME KIDS
IN HER NEIGHBORHOOD

18:19.533 --> 18:22.769
TOOK A HAND AX
TO HER ELECTRICAL CABLES.

18:22.803 --> 18:23.904
I HAD TO DRIVE OVER THERE

18:23.937 --> 18:26.206
AND FIGURE OUT
HOW TO HOOK UP A GENERATOR.

18:26.240 --> 18:27.841
YOU'D THINK
THEY'D LEAVE INSTRUCTIONS

18:27.875 --> 18:28.809
ON THOSE DAMN THINGS.

18:28.842 --> 18:30.444
WHERE'S SHE LIVE?

18:30.477 --> 18:31.345
GARDENDALE.

18:31.378 --> 18:34.481
LACY NEEDS TO GET HERSELF
A NEW ADDRESS.

18:34.515 --> 18:36.750
THAT'S WHAT
SHE'S COMING AROUND TO.

18:36.783 --> 18:39.086
CONRAD,
DID YOU SAY SOMETHING?

18:39.119 --> 18:40.921
OH, NO, JUST GETTIN'
MISSES HERE SOME COFFEE.

18:40.954 --> 18:43.223
"SHO 'NUFF,"
MISS HEYLIA, MA'AM.

18:43.257 --> 18:45.526
WHO'S HAVING A PICNIC?

18:45.559 --> 18:47.327
I AM.

18:47.361 --> 18:50.664
I CAN'T REMEMBER
THE LAST TIME I HAD A PICNIC.

18:53.967 --> 18:55.769
OH, GOD, THAT'S GOOD.

18:55.802 --> 18:58.539
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

18:58.572 --> 19:00.841
THERE'S TWO OF THEM. TWO.

19:00.874 --> 19:02.042
HELLO.

19:02.075 --> 19:04.478
OH, HEY, HONEY.

19:04.511 --> 19:05.913
CALM DOWN.

19:05.946 --> 19:08.782
CALM DOWN.

19:08.815 --> 19:09.783
I'M COMING.

19:09.816 --> 19:11.585
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

19:11.618 --> 19:13.153
THAT LACY?
NO.

19:13.187 --> 19:15.489
I NEED MY STUFF.
IT'S ALMOST READY.

19:15.522 --> 19:16.557
I NEED IT NOW.
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO
GIVE ME A SECOND.

19:16.590 --> 19:19.159
I'LL COME BACK
FOR IT LATER.

19:32.940 --> 19:33.941
WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN?

19:33.974 --> 19:35.075
I'M HERE.
WHAT HAPPENED?

19:35.108 --> 19:36.210
WHERE WERE YOU?

19:36.243 --> 19:38.679
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOUR FACE?

19:38.712 --> 19:40.747
I JUST WANTED TO SEE MEGAN.

19:40.781 --> 19:41.849
CALM DOWN.

19:41.882 --> 19:44.017
SHE HASN'T BEEN IN SCHOOL
FOR TWO DAYS.

19:44.051 --> 19:45.652
THEY TOOK HER TO A CLINIC.

19:45.686 --> 19:47.921
SHE WON'T ANSWER MY MESSAGES.

19:47.955 --> 19:49.690
I‐I JUST WANTED
TO TALK TO HER.

19:49.723 --> 19:50.858
I JUST WANTED TO TALK TO HER,

19:50.891 --> 19:53.260
AND HE WON'T LET ME TALK TO HER,
AND HE HIT ME.

19:53.293 --> 19:54.428
HIT YOU?

19:54.461 --> 19:55.495
WHO?

19:55.529 --> 19:57.164
Man: I DID.

20:01.068 --> 20:02.903
YOU HIT MY KID?

20:02.936 --> 20:04.972
I ONLY WANTED TO TALK TO HER.

20:05.906 --> 20:07.808
YOU HIT MY KID?

20:07.841 --> 20:10.744
YOUR SON
FUCKING STABBED ME.

20:10.777 --> 20:12.446
HE PUT HIS FOOT
THROUGH THE WINDOW,

20:12.479 --> 20:13.514
I GRABBED AHOLD OF HIM,

20:13.547 --> 20:15.949
AND HE GRABBED A PIECE OF GLASS,
AND HE STABBED ME,

20:15.983 --> 20:17.384
SO, YES, I HIT HIM.

20:17.417 --> 20:18.752
SILAS?

20:18.785 --> 20:21.588
KEEP HIM AWAY
FROM MY DAUGHTER.

20:22.923 --> 20:24.625
YOUR SON'S A FUCKING LOSER.

20:24.658 --> 20:26.693
YOU TAUGHT ME HOW TO DRIVE.

20:26.727 --> 20:28.629
SILAS, GET IN THE CAR.

20:39.806 --> 20:41.675
HE JUST
WANTED TO TALK TO HER.

20:41.708 --> 20:43.110
WHAT'S THE BIG FUCKING DEAL?

20:43.143 --> 20:44.378
THE BIG DEAL, MRS. BOTWIN,

20:44.411 --> 20:46.680
IS THAT I HAD A DECENT,
RESPECTABLE DAUGHTER.

20:46.713 --> 20:47.881
OH, PLEASE.

20:47.915 --> 20:49.583
SHE MEETS YOUR SON.
SHE STARTS SMOKING POT.

20:49.616 --> 20:51.585
SHE'S DOING ECSTASY,
AND SHE'S HAVING ABORTIONS.

20:51.618 --> 20:54.121
BEFORE SILAS, SHE WAS THE
BLOWJOB QUEEN OF DEWEY STREET.

20:54.154 --> 20:55.589
AND YOU'RE A SHITTY PARENT.

20:57.024 --> 21:01.595
YOU LAY A HAND ON MY KID AGAIN,
I WILL KILL YOU.

21:01.628 --> 21:02.896
DO YOU UNDERSTAND ME?

21:02.930 --> 21:04.865
ARE YOU FUCKING HEARING ME?

21:04.898 --> 21:07.868
YOU NEED TO LEAVE NOW.

21:07.901 --> 21:10.470
WE'RE LEAVING.
WE ARE COMPLETELY LEAVING.

21:15.209 --> 21:17.678
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

21:20.047 --> 21:22.649
JUST DRIVE.

21:22.683 --> 21:24.318
JUST DRIVE.

21:26.086 --> 21:29.356
AND YOU CAN MAKE
THAT CHOICE FOR CHANGE

21:29.389 --> 21:32.860
BY GIVING ME YOUR VOTE
ON ELECTION DAY.

21:32.893 --> 21:34.194
AND, WHEN ELECTED,

21:34.228 --> 21:38.131
I PROMISE TO BE EVERYTHING
THAT DOUG WILSON IS NOT ‐‐

21:38.165 --> 21:42.202
ACTIVE, COMMITTED, ENGAGED.

21:43.804 --> 21:45.806
ACE.

21:45.839 --> 21:48.408
THANK YOU.

21:48.442 --> 21:51.945
[ LIGHT APPLAUSE ]

21:51.979 --> 21:54.348
Moderator: MR. WILSON,
YOUR FINAL STATEMENT.

21:54.381 --> 21:55.949
NAH, I'M GOOD.

21:55.983 --> 21:57.951
[ APPLAUSE ]

21:57.985 --> 22:00.654
Man: GO, DOUG!

22:05.459 --> 22:07.594
[ SPEAKING SPANISH
INDISTINCTLY ]

22:12.799 --> 22:14.735
HEY, SANJAY.

22:14.768 --> 22:16.470
HEY, ANDY.

22:16.503 --> 22:18.071
WHAT'S THAT HUMMING SOUND?

22:18.105 --> 22:19.239
THE GENERATORS.

22:19.273 --> 22:21.074
THE ARMENIANS
CUT THE ELECTRICAL CABLES.

22:21.108 --> 22:22.910
WELL,
THAT'S NOT VERY NEIGHBORLY.

22:22.943 --> 22:25.078
THEY'RE A HISTORICALLY
PUT‐UPON PEOPLE.

22:25.112 --> 22:27.714
IT'S NOT NEIGHBORLY,
BUT IT'S UNDERSTANDABLE.

22:27.748 --> 22:29.016
WHY ARE YOU STANDING
LIKE THAT?

22:29.049 --> 22:31.385
IT'S THE ONLY WAY
TO GET CHANNEL 12.

22:31.418 --> 22:32.753
OH.

22:32.786 --> 22:34.755
THANKS.

22:34.788 --> 22:36.823
[ STATIC ]

22:36.857 --> 22:39.826
WE ALSO GET CHANNEL 34,
INFOMERCIALS,

22:39.860 --> 22:42.396
AND YOU DON'T HAVE TO HOLD
THE ANTENNA.

22:42.429 --> 22:45.232
I BOUGHT DIAMONIQUE EARRINGS
FOR NANCY.

22:46.099 --> 22:47.668
I MEAN MY MOTHER.

22:48.602 --> 22:50.237
GOOD NIGHT.

22:50.270 --> 22:52.039
NIGHT.

22:57.711 --> 23:00.080
Woman: ...THIS IS
A BEAUTIFUL COMMEMORATIVE SET

23:00.113 --> 23:01.615
OF BABY JESUS SINGING BOWLS.

23:01.648 --> 23:04.284
EACH WERE HANDCRAFTED
IN SANTA FE, NEW MEXICO,

23:04.318 --> 23:06.553
AND SIGNED
BY THE ORIGINAL ARTIST.

23:06.587 --> 23:10.490
THE GREAT THING ABOUT THESE
SINGING BOWLS, ROGER, IS THAT ‐‐

23:10.524 --> 23:12.192
[ CAR TIRES SCREECHING ]

23:14.862 --> 23:16.496
IT'S A RAID.

23:16.530 --> 23:17.364
WHAT?

23:17.397 --> 23:19.266
THE COPS
ARE OUTSIDE EVERYWHERE.

23:19.299 --> 23:20.767
THEY'RE ALL OVER THE PLACE,
ANDY.

23:20.801 --> 23:23.470
WHAT DO WE DO?

23:24.838 --> 23:26.306
SHIT.

23:26.340 --> 23:27.274
SHIT! SHIT!

23:27.307 --> 23:29.409
WHAT DO WE DO?
I DON'T KNOW.

23:29.443 --> 23:31.845
WE GOT TO HIDE IT!
WE GOT TO HIDE IT ALL!

23:31.879 --> 23:33.514
OKAY, OKAY, OKAY.

23:33.547 --> 23:34.681
OW, OW.

23:34.715 --> 23:36.783
WE CAN'T TURN ON THE LIGHTS.
WE'LL RUIN THE GROW CYCLE.

23:36.817 --> 23:38.619
TURN ON THE LIGHTS, SANJAY!

23:38.652 --> 23:40.654
CONRAD SAID NEVER TURN
ON THE LIGHTS AT NIGHT.

23:40.687 --> 23:42.356
FUCK CONRAD!

23:42.389 --> 23:44.491
OKAY. GOD DAMN IT.
ALL RIGHT.

23:44.525 --> 23:45.592
Shh.

23:45.626 --> 23:47.828
PLANTS.

23:47.861 --> 23:48.862
SHIT!

23:48.896 --> 23:50.430
SHIT! SHIT!

23:50.464 --> 23:53.133
GET THE PLANTS.
YOU BETTER GET THE PLANTS!

23:58.372 --> 23:59.339
WHAT DO I DO?

23:59.373 --> 24:01.341
FLUSH EVERYTHING.
I GOT TO SAVE THE MOTHER!

24:01.375 --> 24:03.010
IF YOU TAKE
THE PRAYER STICK

24:03.043 --> 24:05.078
AND STIR IT AROUND
THE OUTSIDE RIM OF THE BOWL,

24:05.112 --> 24:07.748
NOT ONLY DOES IT MAKE
A BEAUTIFUL SOUND...

24:07.781 --> 24:10.017
[ SIRENS WAILING ]

24:10.050 --> 24:11.552
[ TOILET FLUSHING ]

24:11.585 --> 24:12.819
[ GRUNTS ]

24:12.853 --> 24:15.322
[ PRAYING IN HINDI ]

24:20.594 --> 24:22.729
NO. OH, NO.

24:22.763 --> 24:25.098
[ DOGS BARKING IN DISTANCE ]

24:25.132 --> 24:27.601
Woman: ...THE BABY JESUS
BLINKS HIS EYES.

24:27.634 --> 24:28.635
ISN'T THAT PRECIOUS?

24:28.669 --> 24:31.238
[ SIRENS WAILING,
HELICOPTER BLADES WHIRRING ]

24:31.271 --> 24:33.106
FORGIVE ME.

24:49.723 --> 24:52.626
WE HAD THIS PREGNANT HAMSTER
IN SCIENCE CLASS LAST YEAR,

24:52.659 --> 24:55.429
AND DENNY CORWIN
STUCK A PENCIL UP HER BUTT,

24:55.462 --> 24:59.032
AND LATER SHE HAD DEAD BABIES,
KIND OF LIKE AN ABORTION.

25:01.902 --> 25:03.871
FUCK YOU.

25:03.904 --> 25:07.107
IT WAS NOT A FUCKING HAMSTER.

25:08.141 --> 25:11.378
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

25:11.411 --> 25:12.479
[ SIGHS ]

25:12.513 --> 25:13.514
SHANE.

25:13.547 --> 25:14.615
WHAT?

25:14.648 --> 25:18.819
I DON'T WANT YOU PLAYING
WITH DENNY CORWIN ANYMORE.

25:18.852 --> 25:20.220
GO GET READY FOR SCHOOL.

25:22.890 --> 25:25.659
[ TELEPHONE RINGING ]

25:30.364 --> 25:31.798
HELLO?

25:31.832 --> 25:33.333
I HAVE A GIFT FOR YOU.

25:36.003 --> 25:37.404
YOU DO?

25:37.437 --> 25:38.238
YEAH.

25:38.272 --> 25:39.840
Turn on your TV, channel 8.

25:39.873 --> 25:41.308
ALL RIGHT.

25:41.341 --> 25:42.609
I'D HURRY.

25:45.646 --> 25:48.415
Lynette: THE DARING RAID
ON FOUR MARIJUANA GROW HOUSES

25:48.448 --> 25:50.817
TOOK PLACE LATE LAST NIGHT
IN GARDENDALE.

25:50.851 --> 25:52.119
RESIDENTS WERE AWAKENED

25:52.152 --> 25:54.321
TO THE SOUNDS OF POLICE SIRENS
AND BATTERING RAMS.

25:54.354 --> 25:57.157
OVER 1,000 PLANTS
WERE CONFISCATED,

25:57.191 --> 25:59.092
AND DOZENS WERE ARRESTED,

25:59.126 --> 26:01.795
INCLUDING DRUG KINGPIN
ARAM KESHESHIAN.

26:01.828 --> 26:04.097
I'M HERE LIVE
WITH AGENT PETER SCOTTSON

26:04.131 --> 26:05.499
FROM THE DRUG‐ENFORCEMENT
AGENCY.

26:05.532 --> 26:08.268
HE LED THIS RAID.
HE JOINS US NOW. AGENT SCOTTSON?

26:08.302 --> 26:10.170
HANG ON JUST A SECOND,
WILL YOU?

26:10.204 --> 26:12.639
LIEUTENANT SCOTTSON,
CAN YOU TELL US,

26:12.673 --> 26:15.542
IS THIS A COMMON BASE
OF OPERATION FOR DRUG DEALERS?

26:15.576 --> 26:19.146
GATED COMMUNITIES
CAN PROVIDE THE PERFECT COVER

26:19.179 --> 26:20.881
FOR A DRUG OPERATION ‐‐

26:20.914 --> 26:23.016
INSULATION
FROM THE OUTSIDE WORLD.

26:23.050 --> 26:26.520
BUT THEY CAN ALSO PROVIDE
THE IDEAL ENVIRONMENT

26:26.553 --> 26:28.088
FOR A WELL‐EXECUTED BUST.

26:28.121 --> 26:29.890
GATES KEEP PEOPLE OUT,

26:29.923 --> 26:32.226
BUT THEY CAN ALSO
KEEP PEOPLE IN.

26:32.259 --> 26:35.028
IN THIS CASE,
AN ARMENIAN DRUG CARTEL.

26:35.062 --> 26:38.165
I'M NOT SURE
I WOULD USE THE TERM "CARTEL,"

26:38.198 --> 26:40.234
BUT NO DOUBT
IT WAS A MAJOR OPERATION.

26:40.267 --> 26:43.403
THIS IS
A DRUG‐FREE ZONE NOW.

26:43.437 --> 26:44.838
OKAY. THANK YOU.

26:44.872 --> 26:46.306
AGENT SCOTTSON
FROM THE D. E. A.

26:46.340 --> 26:48.742
REPORTING LIVE FROM THE SCENE,
I'M LYNETTE ROMERO.

